<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="isalpha" id="isalpha">isalpha</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cctype&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">isalpha</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> ch <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

La funcion isalpha() retorna un numero distinto de cero si el argumento es una letra
del alfabeto. De lo contrario, retorna cero.
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     <span class="kw4">char</span> c<span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="kw3">scanf</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;%c&quot;</span>, <span class="sy3">&amp;</span>c <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="kw1">if</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw3">isalpha</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span>c<span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>
       <span class="kw3">printf</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Haz ingresado una letra del alfabeto<span class="es1">\n</span>&quot;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
